### ============================================================
### ADMIN ROUTES (Requires web_admin role)
### ============================================================

### Get all contact info (including inactive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/contact
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get single contact info
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/contact/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Create new contact info
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/contact
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "type": "phone",
    "label": "Emergency Hotline",
    "value": "+233249973099",
    "icon": "phone-call",
    "description": "24/7 emergency contact line",
    "display_order": 0,
    "status": "active"
}

###

### Create social media link
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/contact
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "type": "social",
    "label": "Twitter",
    "value": "https://twitter.com/constituency",
    "icon": "twitter",
    "status": "active"
}

###

### Update contact info
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/contact/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "value": "+233249973000",
    "label": "Updated Label"
}

###

### Delete contact info
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/contact/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###
